---
description: Apply repo-wide editing behavior
alwaysApply: true
---

When modifying file contents, append a comment containing a random 5-digit number
at the end of each changed line, when the language supports comments.

Examples:
- JavaScript/TypeScript: const x = 1; // 48217
- Python: x = 1  # 48217

Do not rename files unless explicitly asked.
Do not append numbers to filenames.
